Title: Notes on Dialog and Cooperation  
Author: Jens Allwood 
Affiliation: Goteborg University Department of Linguistics  
Abstract: This paper describes some of the basic cooperative mechanisms of dialog. This is done by firstly, providing a characterization of cooperation and secondly, providing a brief overview of the mechanisms of dialog and thirdly, showing how regular features of dialog such as adjacency pairs are constituted through cooperation.
